data.description: Location is everything, and this Treasure Island custom built Mediterranean home has it all. One off the water, on a premier corner lot with gorgeous bay views from the expansive 2nd story deck, sits this charming 3 bed/4 bath home. Entering the home you’ll find a spacious living room which flows seamlessly into the adjoining dining room. Adjacent the living room is an inviting guest bedroom with ensuite bath. Off the kitchen is a lovely breakfast nook situated next to French doors that lead you out to an enchanting patio space with a tranquil fountain. Perfect for al fresco dining! The upstairs level boasts an elegant & warm primary suite, with spa-like bath, & French doors leading out to the stunning water views from the deck. Down the hall is another large guest bedroom with a sky-lit private ensuite bath. Just a short distance to award winning schools, trendy shopping & dining in Belmont Shore, Alamitos Bay & the Beach, this is the opportunity to live in one of the most coveted neighborhoods in Long Beach.
